  Locus:
    Page: 27
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Atheism
---
A man may believe in all the churches in the world; he may carry in his head
all the sacred books ever written; he may baptize himself in all the rivers
of the earth -- still if he has no perception of God, I would class him with
the rank atheist.
